juniDvmrpMIB.name: juniDvmrpMIB

revisions.description: Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names. Added support for unicast routing and the interface announce list name.
Initial version of this MIB module.

juniDvmrpMIB.contactinfo: Juniper Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886-3146 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 Email: mib@Juniper.net
juniDvmrpMIB.description: The Enterprise MIB module for management of Juniper DVMRP routers.

juniDvmrpAdminState.name: juniDvmrpAdminState
juniDvmrpAdminState.description: Controls whether DVMRP is enabled or not.

juniDvmrpMcastAdminState.name: juniDvmrpMcastAdminState
juniDvmrpMcastAdminState.description: Whether multicast is enabled or not. This is settable via the multicast component.

juniDvmrpRouteHogNotification.name: juniDvmrpRouteHogNotification
juniDvmrpRouteHogNotification.description: The number of routes allowed within a 1 minute interval before a trap is issued warning that there may be a route surge going on.

juniDvmrpRouteLimit.name: juniDvmrpRouteLimit
juniDvmrpRouteLimit.description: The limit on the number of routes that may be advertised on a DVMRP interface.

juniDvmrpS32PrunesOnly.name: juniDvmrpS32PrunesOnly
juniDvmrpS32PrunesOnly.description: Identifies when DVMRP is sending prunes and grafts with only a 32 bit source masks.

juniDvmrpUnicastRouting.name: juniDvmrpUnicastRouting
juniDvmrpUnicastRouting.description: Enable/disable the unicast routing portion of the DVMRP.

juniDvmrpAclDistNbrTable.name: juniDvmrpAclDistNbrTable
juniDvmrpAclDistNbrTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the access lists distance for a list of neighbors.

juniDvmrpAclDistNbrEntry.name: juniDvmrpAclDistNbrEntry
juniDvmrpAclDistNbrEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the juniDvmrpAclDistNbrTable.

juniDvmrpAclDistNbrIfIndex.name: juniDvmrpAclDistNbrIfIndex
juniDvmrpAclDistNbrIfIndex.description: The ifIndex value of the interface for which DVMRP is enabled.

juniDvmrpAclDistNbrAclListName.name: juniDvmrpAclDistNbrAclListName
juniDvmrpAclDistNbrAclListName.description: The name of the access list to be used in the filter.

juniDvmrpAclDistNbrDistance.name: juniDvmrpAclDistNbrDistance
juniDvmrpAclDistNbrDistance.description: The administritive distance metric that will be used

juniDvmrpAclDistNbrNbrListName.name: juniDvmrpAclDistNbrNbrListName
juniDvmrpAclDistNbrNbrListName.description: This is the access list of nbrs for this accept-filter to be applied, this field must be supplied when the row is created

juniDvmrpLocalAddrTable.name: juniDvmrpLocalAddrTable
juniDvmrpLocalAddrTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the local addresses. This is used to retrive all of the addresses configured on a DVMRP interface.

juniDvmrpLocalAddrTableEntry.name: juniDvmrpLocalAddrTableEntry
juniDvmrpLocalAddrTableEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the juniDvmrpLocalAddrTable.

juniDvmrpLocalAddrIfIndex.name: juniDvmrpLocalAddrIfIndex
juniDvmrpLocalAddrIfIndex.description: The ifIndex value of the interface for which DVMRP is enabled.

juniDvmrpLocalAddrAddrOrIfIndex.name: juniDvmrpLocalAddrAddrOrIfIndex
juniDvmrpLocalAddrAddrOrIfIndex.description: For unnumbered interfaces, this takes on the value of the ifIndex. For numbered interfaces, this is the address of one of the addresses associated with the interface.

juniDvmrpLocalAddrMask.name: juniDvmrpLocalAddrMask
juniDvmrpLocalAddrMask.description: The IP Address mask associated with this entry.

juniDvmrpSummaryAddrTable.name: juniDvmrpSummaryAddrTable
juniDvmrpSummaryAddrTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the DVMRP summary addresses. This is used to retrive all of the summary address configured on a DVMRP interface.

juniDvmrpSummaryAddrTableEntry.name: juniDvmrpSummaryAddrTableEntry
juniDvmrpSummaryAddrTableEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the juniDvmrpSummaryAddrTable.

juniDvmrpSummaryAddrIfIndex.name: juniDvmrpSummaryAddrIfIndex
juniDvmrpSummaryAddrIfIndex.description: The ifIndex value of the interface for which DVMRP is enabled.

juniDvmrpSummaryAddrAddress.name: juniDvmrpSummaryAddrAddress
juniDvmrpSummaryAddrAddress.description: This is the summary address that will be created.

juniDvmrpSummaryAddrMask.name: juniDvmrpSummaryAddrMask
juniDvmrpSummaryAddrMask.description: The mask of the summary address to be created.

juniDvmrpSummaryAddrCost.name: juniDvmrpSummaryAddrCost
juniDvmrpSummaryAddrCost.description: The administritive distance metric used to actually calculate distance vectors.

juniDvmrpInterfaceTable.name: juniDvmrpInterfaceTable
juniDvmrpInterfaceTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the router's multicast-capable interfaces. This table augments the DvmrpInterfaceTable.

juniDvmrpInterfaceEntry.name: juniDvmrpInterfaceEntry
juniDvmrpInterfaceEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the juniDvmrpInterfaceTable. This row extends ipMRouteInterfaceEntry in the IP Multicast MIB, where the threshold object resides.

juniDvmrpInterfaceAutoSummary.name: juniDvmrpInterfaceAutoSummary
juniDvmrpInterfaceAutoSummary.description: Enables or disable auto-summarization on this interface.

juniDvmrpInterfaceMetricOffsetOut.name: juniDvmrpInterfaceMetricOffsetOut
juniDvmrpInterfaceMetricOffsetOut.description: The distance metric for this interface which is used to calculate outbound distance vectors.

juniDvmrpInterfaceMetricOffsetIn.name: juniDvmrpInterfaceMetricOffsetIn
juniDvmrpInterfaceMetricOffsetIn.description: The distance metric for this interface which is used to calculate inbound distance vectors.

juniDvmrpInterfaceAdminState.name: juniDvmrpInterfaceAdminState
juniDvmrpInterfaceAdminState.description: Controls whether DVMRP is enabled or not.

juniDvmrpInterfaceAnnounceListName.name: juniDvmrpInterfaceAnnounceListName
juniDvmrpInterfaceAnnounceListName.description: Configures the name of the acceptance announce filter for the IP access list.

juniDvmrpPruneTable.name: juniDvmrpPruneTable
juniDvmrpPruneTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the router's upstream prune state.

juniDvmrpPruneEntry.name: juniDvmrpPruneEntry
juniDvmrpPruneEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the juniDvmrpPruneTable.

juniDvmrpPruneGroup.name: juniDvmrpPruneGroup
juniDvmrpPruneGroup.description: The group address which has been pruned.

juniDvmrpPruneSource.name: juniDvmrpPruneSource
juniDvmrpPruneSource.description: The address of the source or source network which has been pruned.

juniDvmrpPruneSourceMask.name: juniDvmrpPruneSourceMask
juniDvmrpPruneSourceMask.description: The address of the source or source network which has been pruned. The mask must either be all 1's, or else juniDvmrpPruneSource and juniDvmrpPruneSourceMask must match juniDvmrpRouteSource and juniDvmrpRouteSourceMask for some entry in the juniDvmrpRouteTable.

juniDvmrpPruneIIFIfIndex.name: juniDvmrpPruneIIFIfIndex
juniDvmrpPruneIIFIfIndex.description: The ifIndex of the upstream interface for this source group entry.

juniDvmrpPruneUpTime.name: juniDvmrpPruneUpTime
juniDvmrpPruneUpTime.description: This is the amount of time that this prune has remained valid.

juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifTable.name: juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifTable
juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifTable.description: The (conceptual) OIFs for particular source group entries.

juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifEntry.name: juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifEntry
juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifTable.

juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifGroup.name: juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifGroup
juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifGroup.description: The group address which has been pruned.

juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifSource.name: juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifSource
juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifSource.description: The address of the source or source network which has been pruned.

juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifSourceMask.name: juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifSourceMask
juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifSourceMask.description: The address of the source or source network which has been pruned. The mask must either be all 1's, or else juniDvmrpPruneSource and juniDvmrpPruneSourceMask must match juniDvmrpRouteSource and juniDvmrpRouteSourceMask for some entry in the juniDvmrpRouteTable.

juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifOIFIfIndex.name: juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifOIFIfIndex
juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifOIFIfIndex.description: The ifIndex of one of the downstream interfaces for this source group entry.

juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifOIFPruned.name: juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifOIFPruned
juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifOIFPruned.description: If true this OIF has been pruned.

juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifOIFDnTTL.name: juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifOIFDnTTL
juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifOIFDnTTL.description: The timeout for this OIF. If juniDvmrpSrcGrpOifOIFPruned is false then this is undefined.

juniDvmrpRouteHogNotificationTrap.name: juniDvmrpRouteHogNotificationTrap
juniDvmrpRouteHogNotificationTrap.description: This is an indication that the route hog notification limit has been exceeded during the past minute. It may mean that a route surge is going on.

juniDvmrpCompliance.name: juniDvmrpCompliance
juniDvmrpCompliance.description: Obsolete compliance statement for entities which implement the Juniper DVMRP MIB. This statement became obsolete when new objects were added.

juniDvmrpCompliance2.name: juniDvmrpCompliance2
juniDvmrpCompliance2.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the Juniper DVMRP MIB.

juniDvmrpBaseGroup.name: juniDvmrpBaseGroup
juniDvmrpBaseGroup.description: Obsolete collection of objects providing basic management of DVMRP in a Juniper product. This group became obsolete when support was added for the DVMRP unicast routing object.

juniDvmrpAclDistNbrGroup.name: juniDvmrpAclDistNbrGroup
juniDvmrpAclDistNbrGroup.description: A collection of objects providing management of DVMRP access list distance neighbors in a Juniper product.

juniDvmrpInterfaceGroup.name: juniDvmrpInterfaceGroup
juniDvmrpInterfaceGroup.description: Obsolete collection of objects providing management of a DVMRP interface in a Juniper product. This group became obsolete when support for the DVMRP interface announce list name object was added.

juniDvmrpSourceGroup.name: juniDvmrpSourceGroup
juniDvmrpSourceGroup.description: A collection of objects providing management of a DVMRP source group in a Juniper product.

juniDvmrpNotificationGroup.name: juniDvmrpNotificationGroup
juniDvmrpNotificationGroup.description: A notification for signaling important DVMRP events.

juniDvmrpBaseGroup2.name: juniDvmrpBaseGroup2
juniDvmrpBaseGroup2.description: A collection of objects providing basic management of DVMRP in a Juniper product.

juniDvmrpInterfaceGroup2.name: juniDvmrpInterfaceGroup2
juniDvmrpInterfaceGroup2.description: A collection of objects providing management of a DVMRP interface in a Juniper product.
